{"tid":1633444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有無人諗過擺返街站派傳單","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T21:13:04.000Z","uid":306098,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a470bb29ccca49865ec1670163f93a7e1633d5af","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"依家我哋要做既，就係多番文宣，走出同溫層。<br />\n連儂牆已經開始係俾自己人圍爐或者淺藍，所謂冷感既港豬已經唔再care，甚至覺得連儂牆都係啲暴徒所為而唔再去睇。我地要贏就一定要走出同溫層，街站可以同啲淺藍理性溝通，或者再多多一個渠道去解釋我地依家做既野。街站都唔一定係最好既方法，所以歡迎手足討論如何<span style=\"font-size: large;\">走出同溫層</span><br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"db48bf75a22a3a56feb4064dfe993081796858f0","tid":1633444,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"值得做！幫推<br />\n有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"92c0459bdcf8d54ca9f2adf7b3c752ee4bac0341","tid":1633444,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dO7Z2OW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdO7Z2OW.jpg&h=925cce53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxJ20AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxJ20AB.jpg&h=c7141e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFpQ9Cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFpQ9Cb.jpg&h=a7156522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"424da5510f0b8f91c7c018cbf914629c4c453da4","tid":1633444,"uid":295813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"街站我支持"},{"pid":"227abc56c04a268c107d8c345d680eb6c1b0c6be","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:07:10.000Z","msg":"幫p牌推啊"},{"pid":"6d18dd75580b02e2ff89005496c79ebb0be6f3f8","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"雖然我知同藍絲理性好on9 但係都要諗方法走出同溫層"},{"pid":"1e3ab089baa8ca3e49eb34324055be82944c9fb5","tid":1633444,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:08:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！ 而家只係要你入黎推post</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"5395a9e1208eef4b17cb2572f1cfff97b83b6431","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"829c4e2b313b00c8901768dcf136e5bc26050349","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"cd7eb2c4aed7c31419117e7b5e3e33c0a2492b0f","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"d705e7245f33f6568bd0dd2b5423add8f5fde503","tid":1633444,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"有諗過放張凳喺地鐵站口，入面有晒唔同文宣，搵啲識講嘢既和理非輪更<br />\n不過諗唔到點處理安全問題"},{"pid":"5e63ea30b3ad66f9e965fce53bac230e0fa2794f","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"搵啲可以理性既手足去輪更啊"},{"pid":"52761163744ecfd7e94bdda870d53043ff11327b","tid":1633444,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"推到民陣入黎！一人一票對林女士提出不信任動議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8992a0aa5536b9f712744252b6426a80e1f04b4e","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"唔洗勇武啊 依家要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">走出同溫層啊</span>"},{"pid":"5e81bfd3d6996b005990e2040fa971f6110e0bdf","tid":1633444,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f94c765cfa83eaa4dfb019f47367d663df6ea01","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"大大力推啊"},{"pid":"3122c51bd06664d0390109bf60a0b614be00348b","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"順便俾個機會和理非做嘢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bd1caaff8a8fc95733ab4a470652cc731f0221","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山啊"},{"pid":"b5bf308fb74187c74b94dee7ef5405e6f8bed8e8","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"幫p牌推啊"},{"pid":"f6ee4fd0a355ec3bb22a76b2cf2c886b36033a0f","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"60b230878b895d3078ee51361264ba8b7225e5ee","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"幫p牌仔推行動post啊"},{"pid":"170fc5ea19101dc4e21713aec10a134de32e355d","tid":1633444,"uid":306098,"like":0,"dis